collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql:
select m.idsigma as codigo, concat( m.ccodcen,'-',p.vobserv,' ', m.vnombre) as nombre from registro.mpoblad m
							inner join public.mconten p
							on m.ctipcen = p.idsigma

select m.idsigma as codigovia, concat( m.ccodvia,'-',p.vobserv,' ', m.vnombre) as nombrevia from registro.mviadis m
							inner join public.mconten p
							on m.ctipvia = p.idsigma
